---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Wraith — Fast, private WireGuard VPN with Haven DNS built in"
  description="Wraith is Katafract's WireGuard VPN. Fleet we operate ourselves, Haven DNS at every exit, kill switch, 5 devices, no logs. Included with Enclave and Sovereign. iOS coming soon."
  ogDescription="Fast, private WireGuard VPN with Haven DNS at every exit. No logs. 5 devices. Included with Enclave ($8/mo) and Sovereign ($18/mo). Coming soon to iOS."
  ogImage="https://katafract.com/images/og-wraith.jpg"
  section="apps"
  twitterCard="summary_large_image"
>
  <style slot="head" is:global>
    /* Wraith brand override — purple accent instead of cyan */
    :root {
      --wraith: #818CF8;
      --wraith-dim: rgba(129,140,248,0.12);
      --wraith-border: rgba(129,140,248,0.2);
      --wraith-glow: rgba(129,140,248,0.06);
    }

    /* App hero */
    .app-hero { padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2.5rem; max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .app-hero-eyebrow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--wraith);
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .app-hero-eyebrow .back-link { color: var(--dim2); letter-spacing: 0.15em; }
    .app-hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.2vw, 3.75rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .app-hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--wraith); }
    .app-hero .tagline {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 620px;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .app-hero .trust-line {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    }

    /* App main container */
    .app-main { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 5rem; }

    .app-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .btn-appstore {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: white;
      color: #050510;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-appstore:hover { background: #e8e8e8; text-decoration: none; }

    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      background: var(--wraith-dim);
      color: var(--wraith);
      border: 1px solid var(--wraith-border);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.18); text-decoration: none; }

    .price-note {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    /* Live badge */
    .live-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      color: #33E8A0;
      background: rgba(51,232,160,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(51,232,160,0.18);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .live-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #33E8A0;
      animation: pulse-green 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse-green {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.35; }
    }

    /* Divider */
    .section-divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 3.5rem 0;
    }

    /* Features */
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--wraith-glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover { border-color: var(--wraith-border); }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .feature-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
    .feature-desc {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* Section headings */
    .app-page-section { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .app-section-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      color: var(--wraith);
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .app-section-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .app-section-sub {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    /* Why block — Tek voice */
    .why-block {
      background: var(--wraith-glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--wraith-border);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 2rem 2rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    }
    .why-block p {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin: 0 0 0.9rem 0;
    }
    .why-block p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .why-block .attribution {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* How-it-works trust rows */
    .trust-rows {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .trust-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr;
      gap: 1.1rem;
      align-items: start;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.55);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.875rem;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .trust-row:hover { border-color: var(--wraith-border); }
    .trust-row .step-num {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--wraith);
      background: var(--wraith-dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--wraith-border);
      border-radius: 999px;
      width: 42px;
      height: 24px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
    .trust-row h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0 0 0.3rem;
    }
    .trust-row p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .trust-row a { color: var(--wraith); }

    /* Use-case cards */
    .scenario-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .scenario-card {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.35rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.875rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.55);
    }
    .scenario-card .scenario-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      color: var(--wraith);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .scenario-card p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Proof row */
    .proof-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.85rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem;
    }
    .proof-link {
      display: block;
      padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.45);
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .proof-link:hover { border-color: var(--wraith-border); background: var(--wraith-glow); text-decoration: none; }
    .proof-link .proof-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      color: var(--wraith);
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .proof-link .proof-name {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .proof-link .proof-desc {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      margin-top: 0.2rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Pricing */
    .pricing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(230px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .plan-card {
      background: rgba(10,10,20,0.5);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .plan-card.featured {
      background: var(--wraith-glow);
      border-color: var(--wraith-border);
    }
    .plan-label {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
    }
    .plan-card.featured .plan-label { color: var(--wraith); }
    .plan-price {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .plan-cadence {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
      margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .plan-features {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.86rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .plan-features li.hi { color: var(--text); }
    .plan-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid var(--wraith-border);
      background: var(--wraith-dim);
      color: var(--wraith);
      transition: background 0.15s;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .plan-cta:hover { background: rgba(129,140,248,0.22); text-decoration: none; }
    .plan-card.featured .plan-cta {
      background: var(--wraith);
      color: #0a0a14;
      border-color: var(--wraith);
    }
    .plan-card.featured .plan-cta:hover { background: #a3abf9; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
    .faq-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.1rem 0;
    }
    .faq-item summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--text);
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-item summary::after {
      content: '+';
      color: var(--wraith);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .faq-item[open] summary::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .faq-item .faq-body {
      margin-top: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .faq-item .faq-body a { color: var(--wraith); }

    /* Bundle strip */
    .bundle-strip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      background: var(--wraith-glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--wraith-border);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .bundle-strip .bundle-text {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .bundle-strip .bundle-text strong { color: var(--text); }
    .bundle-strip .bundle-apps {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.9rem;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .bundle-strip .bundle-apps span { color: var(--wraith); }

    /* Footer trust triad */
    .footer-trust {
      margin: 2.5rem 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-trust .trust-links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--dim);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }
    .footer-trust .trust-links a { color: var(--wraith); }
    .footer-trust .requires-line {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--dim2);
      margin-top: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .app-hero { padding: 6rem 3.5rem 3rem; }
      .app-main { padding: 0 3.5rem 7rem; }
    }
    @media (min-width: 1100px) {
      .app-hero { padding: 7rem 5rem 3.5rem; }
      .app-main { padding: 0 5rem 8rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .app-hero { padding: 3rem 1.25rem 2rem; }
      .app-main { padding: 0 1.25rem 4rem; }
      .trust-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; }
    }
  </style>

  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
      "name": "Wraith",
      "alternateName": "WraithVPN",
      "applicationCategory": "SecurityApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "iOS 17.0 or later",
      "description": "WireGuard-based VPN built on Katafract-operated WraithGate nodes. Haven DNS at every exit, kill switch, up to 5 devices, no activity logs. Included with Enclave and Sovereign subscriptions.",
      "url": "https://katafract.com/apps/wraith",
      "image": "https://katafract.com/images/og-wraith.jpg",
      "author": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Katafract LLC",
        "url": "https://katafract.com"
      },
      "offers": [
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "name": "Enclave",
          "priceCurrency": "USD",
          "price": "8.00",
          "description": "Included in Enclave subscription — $8/mo or $64/yr",
          "url": "https://buy.stripe.com/bJe28r4JX9TcgjocRqffy04"
        },
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "name": "Sovereign",
          "priceCurrency": "USD",
          "price": "18.00",
          "description": "Included in Sovereign subscription — $18/mo or $144/yr, with multi-hop VPN",
          "url": "https://buy.stripe.com/7sY9ATekx1mG2sydVuffy0h"
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>

  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does Wraith work in countries with DPI or VPN restrictions?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Wraith uses standard WireGuard on UDP, which is fast and modern but is not designed to evade deep-packet-inspection firewalls. If you routinely operate in a jurisdiction that blocks VPN traffic, we're open about that and working on obfuscated transports for a future release."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How fast is Wraith compared to NordVPN or ExpressVPN?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Wraith runs WireGuard — the same protocol most modern VPNs use under the hood. Speed depends on your distance to the nearest exit node. Our fleet covers EU, US, Asia, and is continuously expanding. Haven DNS runs on the node itself, so DNS lookups never leave the tunnel."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How many devices can I use on one account?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Up to 5 devices on Enclave. Unlimited devices on Sovereign. A device is a single install of the Wraith app."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What gets logged?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "No connection timestamps, no assigned-IP records, no DNS query logs, no session durations. The pipelines that would collect those were never built. Details at docs.katafract.io/trust/logs/."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Who's behind Katafract?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Katafract LLC is a small, founder-operated company. We dogfood every app. Source and trust posture are inspectable at github.com/katafract-io and docs.katafract.io/trust/."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does Wraith work with streaming services?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Most services work normally because we operate our own fleet rather than leasing from IP-reputation-poor pools. We don't guarantee specific services will always work — that's outside our control — but we don't go out of our way to break them either."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What happens if my subscription lapses?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Your peer configuration is rotated and the tunnel stops. Haven DNS (free, no account) keeps working. Re-subscribe and your access is restored immediately. We don't keep billing hostages."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>

  <div class="app-hero">
    <div class="app-hero-eyebrow">
      <span>Wraith</span>
      <span>&middot;</span>
      <span class="live-badge">⏳ iOS · In review</span>
      <span>&middot;</span>
      <a href="/" class="back-link">by Katafract &nearr;</a>
    </div>
    <h1>Fast, private WireGuard &mdash;<br>with <em>Haven DNS</em> built in.</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Your traffic rides our own fleet. No logs, no ads, no middlemen &mdash; because the infrastructure to run any of that doesn&rsquo;t exist on our side of the wire.</p>
    <p class="trust-line">Infrastructure built so there&rsquo;s nothing to betray.</p>
    <div class="app-cta-row">
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn-appstore plausible-event-name=subscribe_wraith_coming_soon">Get Enclave — be first in line &rarr;</a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary plausible-event-name=view_wraith_how_it_works">How it works &darr;</a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--dim);">App Store approval in progress. Android? <a href="/android/" style="color: var(--wraith);">Join the waitlist →</a></div>
  </div>

  <main class="app-main">

    <!-- 2. Why we built this -->
    <section class="app-page-section">
      <div class="app-section-label">Why Wraith</div>
      <h2 class="app-section-title">Because the breach-letter cycle is exhausting.</h2>
    </section>
    <div class="why-block">
      <p>I&rsquo;m Tek. I piled up third-party apps for every layer of privacy &mdash; each one another company I had to trust. Every few months another breach letter arrived from a company I&rsquo;d never heard of, holding data a company I <em>did</em> know had moved, sold, or leaked.</p>
      <p>I stopped trusting third parties for the parts that mattered. I didn&rsquo;t want to ask anyone to trust me more than the companies that burned them either. So I built Wraith on infrastructure I operate end-to-end, with a posture that&rsquo;s inspectable rather than opaque.</p>
      <div class="attribution">&mdash; Tek, founder</div>
    </div>

    <hr class="section-divider">

    <!-- 3. What it does -->
    <section class="app-page-section">
      <div class="app-section-label">What Wraith does</div>
      <h2 class="app-section-title">Five things, done carefully.</h2>
    </section>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x26A1;</div>
        <div class="feature-title">WireGuard across a global fleet</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Modern, audited, open protocol. Nodes in EU, US, and Asia &mdash; continuously expanding, not a fixed count.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F6E1;&#xFE0F;</div>
        <div class="feature-title">Haven DNS at every exit</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">Ads, trackers, and known malware domains are blocked at the DNS layer &mdash; before the app on your phone ever sees them.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F512;</div>
        <div class="feature-title">Kill switch</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">If the tunnel drops, traffic is blocked. Nothing leaks to your ISP while the app reconnects.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F4F1;</div>
        <div class="feature-title">Up to 5 devices</div>
